Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后，不断拒绝，直到对方上钩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>And after that, say "no"</i> a <i>lot until the guy is hooked.</i>
