Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗急跳墙的人真好削\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>It was almost scary how easy it could be</i>
