Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛林里夫人，很高兴又见面了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Lady Edith Greensly. It's so good to see you again.
