Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:17:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对申贷人精挑细选\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're very selective.
