Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.09,0:39:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有核发执照和许可\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey. No licenses, no permits.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.76,0:39:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别太贪心，卡尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Quit while you're ahead, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.26,0:39:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识那人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I know the guy... I know the right people
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.93,0:39:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有人能帮你  - 谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}who are going to help you out. Who's the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.43,0:39:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人叫卡迈波里托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The guy is Carmine Polito.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.35,0:39:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迈波里托是谁？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who's Carmine Polito?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.97,0:39:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迈波里托？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>Carmine Polito?</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.93,0:39:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迈波里托，不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Carmine Polito, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.10,0:39:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老板史多达告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>RICHIE: My boss, Stoddard, proceeded to tell me</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.60,0:39:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迈波里托是纽泽西的地方大老\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>that Carmine Polito was the most quietly powerful person in the state of New Jersey.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.07,0:39:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直住在种族混杂的坎登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>A lifetime native of the very racially mixed Camden,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.11,0:39:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里变成了少数民族区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>which had become a ghetto.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.78,0:39:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那里当了十年市长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>And where he had been mayor for ten years.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.03,0:39:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,备受爱戴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>A very beloved guy.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.87,0:39:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对他的民众不离不弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>A guy who never gave up on his people.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.29,0:39:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他父亲是意大利移民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>His father had emigrated from Italy and had stoked coal.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.29,0:39:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是铲煤工人，他一大家子有五个小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>A big family guy with five kids.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.38,0:39:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正粗圆简体}{\c&HA96A13&}{\fs12}(LOUD CHATTER)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.54,0:39:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们甚至又领养了一个孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>They even adopted some other kid, a black kid</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.38,0:39:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个失去家人的黑人小孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>from the Boys and Girls Club who'd lost his family.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.47,0:39:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的家庭充满欢乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>I mean, his household was a joyous place.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.39,0:39:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太太桃丽是他的最爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>And his wife, Dolly, well, she was the apple of his eye.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.64,0:39:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是全家的重心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>And the center of the household.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.10,0:40:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都喜欢这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>I mean, everyone loved this guy.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.15,0:40:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他心胸宽大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>And he had a huge heart.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大萧条期间政府雇用工匠，画了这面墙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}CARMINE: The WPA employed craftsmen to paint this during the Depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.95,0:40:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今我们为何不能雇人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why can't we employ people today
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.42,0:40:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重建大西洋城？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to do work like this in rebuilding Atlantic City?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.49,0:40:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他与工会合作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>RICHIE: He worked with all the unions,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.16,0:40:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是州议会领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>he was the leader of the State Assembly,</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.95,0:40:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让纽泽西赌博合法，创造就业机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>and he had just gotten gambling legalized in New Jersey to create jobs.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.67,0:40:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却争取不到经费重建大西洋城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>But he couldn't get the funds to rebuild Atlantic City.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.71,0:40:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的困扰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>And that was his problem.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.09,0:40:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们的协助下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>So, with our help, he was about to have his hand</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.59,0:40:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在错的时间寻求错的金援\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>in the wrong pocket at the wrong time.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.59,0:40:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说这就是贪腐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}<i>And to me, that meant corrupt.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.93,0:40:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说要逮到骗子，诈欺犯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}STODDARD: You said grifters, con artists.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.39,0:40:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别找政治人物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're not going after some politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.31,0:40:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点子很糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is a bad idea, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.23,0:40:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实很简单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, it's really simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.94,0:40:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要将两百万元存到...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All you need is to put two million in a Chase account...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.65,0:40:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？ 在酋长的名下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What? ...under the sheik's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.44,0:40:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁的两百万？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whose $2 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.82,0:40:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两百万，酋长名下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}$2 million under the sheik's name in a chase account 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.46,0:40:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们控制的帐户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that we control.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.74,0:41:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡迈打电话给银行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Carmine calls up on the telephone,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.25,0:41:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让银行查出真有酋长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}calls the bank and he sees that the sheik is real
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.21,0:41:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且真有帐户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and he has a real account.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.75,0:41:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.55,0:41:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会拿纳税人的两百万\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not taking $2 million of the taxpayers' money,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.59,0:41:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存到任何帐户五天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}putting it anywhere for five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.68,0:41:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管我们能不能控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't care if we control it the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.22,0:41:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史多达，让我们尽力扫除贪腐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Stoddard, let us do what we need to do to rule out corruption
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.33,0:41:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扫除破坏国家体制的公职人员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and to get rid of the payoff guys that are ruining this country. That's my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.56,0:41:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的梦想，请别扼杀它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't smother it, please. You know, Richard,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.35,0:41:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞奇，我明白你很积极\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I understand your eagerness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.73,0:41:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.40,0:41:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是密西根人吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know I'm from Michigan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.19,0:41:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说个故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let me tell you a story
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.69,0:41:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我、我爸和我哥的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}about me and my dad and my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.82,0:41:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们每年11月都去冰钓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We used to go ice fishing every November.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.03,0:41:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ice fishing, that's all anybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.24,0:41:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们所有人的嗜好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's what we lived for.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.53,0:41:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Holy shit. Just listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.08,0:41:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,故事很美，摆个小炉子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's beautiful. You have a little stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.74,0:41:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家挤在一起取暖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You huddle around, you keep each other warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.75,0:41:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钓线放下去就等着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You drop a line and you just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.21,0:41:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一年我哥说：\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}One year, my brother says,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.25,0:41:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们十月去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Let's go in October."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.59,0:41:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十月去冰钓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He wants to go ice fishing in October.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.25,0:41:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸说：不行，冰还太薄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My dad says, "No, the ice is too thin."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.17,0:41:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哥说...我爱我哥，他说...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My brother says, I love my brother, he says...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.09,0:41:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解，你哥走到冰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I understand. Your brother went out on the ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.51,0:41:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果冰太薄掉进湖里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\shad1}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the ice was too thin, he fell through the ice,
